metadata.name: The AlphaBYTEs #1
description: Created by Art by Amrita as part of her The AlphaBYTEs series.
Amrita has reimagined the alphabet using sound, art and NFT’s to create her new language for the the Metaverse and beyond.
The Alphabet reimagined for Web 3.0 + her Signature style of SoundBYTEs = The AlphaBYTEs
“MetaREVERSED” is the first word and collection from the AlphaBYTEs.
Reversing the Metaverse by bringing her digital work to a physical aluminium sculpture to create one of the world’s first physically fractionalised Augmented Reality Sculpture.
- Each NFT comes with a slice of the physical sculpture
- One lucky collector will receive the full word mounted on a steel canvas
- Each NFT is unique and is an image of the full word “MetaREVERSED” with randomised colour coordinations of gold silver and copper
- Only 5 NFT’s are augmented reality enabled
- An all access mint MetaPASS to her NFT Art House - MetaMAISON
metadata.creator: Amrita Sethi
